<br>
I know of three kinds of spells:<br>
<br>
1. ones that permanently belong to you (race bonus, deity bonus, class related spells, etc.)<br>
<br>
2. ones that are on scrolls (can only cast once, then the scroll is used)<br>
<br>
3. ones that are on items (weapon procs, rings, amulets etc.)<br>
<br>
Now, is there a way to find and add spells to the type (1) I have listed above? I have a whole mess of scrolls that I have found around, but they seem to be the 'one time use' scrolls. Is there a spellbook?<br>
<br>
I'd like to focus on illusions, if I can get more spells (a thief with illusions would be a blast to play). Soul Trap would also be good, for enchantment purposes (I really want to make some of my own equipment). <p><FONT SIZE=+1><a href=http://casusbelli.tamu.edu/magelo.php?mid=13102><B>Biggins Black: Assassin</B></a></FONT><BR>
